CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1777471868
OL,3,CMum-of-five says riots were 'worst two
OL,4,Cseconds of my life, but I'm sorry'
OL,6,FStacey Vint, of the town, was
OL,7,Fconvicted of violent disorder and
OL,8,Fsentenced to 20 months in prison
OL,9,Ffollowing the unrest in August 2024,
OL,10,Fwhich was filmed by onlookers.
OL,12,FVideos of her actions went viral
OL,13,Fwithin hours, showing her push the
OL,14,Fwheelie bin into officers before
OL,15,Ffalling over. It went on to be used in
OL,16,Fa number of memes.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1777471868
OL,3,CMum-of-five says riots were 'worst two
OL,4,Cseconds of my life, but I'm sorry'
OL,6,FSpeaking for the first time on TV,
OL,7,FStacey described the incident as "two
OL,8,Fof the worst seconds of my life" as
OL,9,Fshe apologised to the community in
OL,10,FMiddlesbrough.
OL,12,F"Once I'd watched myself and been
OL,13,Fsentenced and stuff, I was laid in my
OL,14,Fprison cell in bed and I thought I'm
OL,15,Fso disgusted in like how I've behaved,
OL,16,Feven though it was literally two of
OL,17,Fthe worst seconds of my life.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1777471868
OL,3,CMum-of-five says riots were 'worst two
OL,4,Cseconds of my life, but I'm sorry'
OL,6,F"I thought all my kids are going to
OL,7,Fsee all that, but it's not even just
OL,8,Fthat bit, I'm going to be known for
OL,9,Fbeing part of a racist riot for the
OL,10,Frest of my life.
OL,12,F"I can't change what happened. All I
OL,13,Fcan do is just tell the truth."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1777471868
OL,3,CMum-of-five says riots were 'worst two
OL,4,Cseconds of my life, but I'm sorry'
OL,6,FStacey said she was in a bad place
OL,7,Femotionally and mentally when the
OL,8,Friots took place, having been homeless
OL,9,Fon and off for years, addicted to
OL,10,Fdrink and drugs since the age of 13,
OL,11,Fand grieving for her grandmother's
OL,12,Fdeath and losing access to her
OL,13,Fchildren.
OL,15,FDespite the circumstances, she was
OL,16,Fadamant that she is not a racist.
OL,18,F"No, (I'm not a racist) not at all,"
OL,19,Fshe said, when challenged about her
OL,20,Fintentions on the day of the unrest.
OL,21,F"It was just the atmosphere I think.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1777471868
OL,3,CMum-of-five says riots were 'worst two
OL,4,Cseconds of my life, but I'm sorry'
OL,6,F"I just felt like I was part of
OL,7,Fsomething, even though it was not
OL,8,Fsomething that you should be proud of
OL,9,Fbeing a part of, because I'm not
OL,10,Fracist or anything, obviously, but I'd
OL,11,Fbeen up drinking and on drugs four
OL,12,Fnights and stuff, so I wasn't thinking
OL,13,Fstraight anyway."
OL,15,FHaving taken part in the riots, pushed
OL,16,Fthe wheelie bin at police and having
OL,17,Fshouted racist slogans, she said she
OL,18,Funderstood why people might not
OL,19,Fbelieve her.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1777471868
OL,3,CMum-of-five says riots were 'worst two
OL,4,Cseconds of my life, but I'm sorry'
OL,6,F"I'm not here to change anyone's
OL,7,Fopinion," she continued. "For the past
OL,8,Flike seven years I've just been living
OL,9,Fhomeless, living anywhere, living in
OL,10,FB&Bs and hotels, drinking, taking
OL,11,Fdrugs.
OL,13,F"That was my life and that was all I
OL,14,Fknew. Once I'd been in jail and I was
OL,15,Fsober and working with bereavement
OL,16,Fcouncillors for my Nana's death and
OL,17,Fthings like that, I realised how like
OL,18,Feasily influenced like I could be, and
OL,19,Fhow much, just because like I heard
OL,20,Fthat one person shouting something,
OL,21,FI've copied them.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1777471868
OL,3,CMum-of-five says riots were 'worst two
OL,4,Cseconds of my life, but I'm sorry'
OL,6,F"So that makes the world think I'm
OL,7,Fthis or that, but like I said, I'm not
OL,8,Fhere to change anyone's opinions, I'm
OL,9,Fjust getting it out there."
OL,11,FWhen on probation following her
OL,12,Frelease, Stacey took part in the Safer
OL,13,FCommunities restorative justice
OL,14,Fprogramme, which is run by Restorative
OL,15,FCleveland.
OL,17,FThe programme has seen 12 of those
OL,18,Finvolved in the Middlesbrough riot
OL,19,Fwrite letters of apology to victims to
OL,20,Fhelp make amends.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1777471868
OL,3,CMum-of-five says riots were 'worst two
OL,4,Cseconds of my life, but I'm sorry'
OL,6,FFor Stacey, it has been life changing.
OL,8,FShe said she was now no longer
OL,9,Fconsuming alcohol or drugs, has
OL,10,Fregained access to her children, and
OL,11,Fis working with one victim of the
OL,12,Friots in schools and workshops to
OL,13,Fshare her experience of the disorder.
OL,15,FIt is hoped her work will deter others
OL,16,Fgetting involved in future unrest.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1777471868
OL,3,CMum-of-five says riots were 'worst two
OL,4,Cseconds of my life, but I'm sorry'
OL,6,FHer former teacher, Satti Collins,
OL,7,Ftold ITV News Tyne Tees that she felt
OL,8,F"frightened" to leave her house for
OL,9,Fdays following the riots, but she
OL,10,Fwanted to reach out to Stacey, via
OL,11,FRestorative Cleveland, to ask her why
OL,12,Fshe did it.
OL,14,F"I was worried for the way the
OL,15,Fcommunity is together in Middlesbrough
OL,16,Fand it breaking down," she said. "So,
OL,17,Fwe got chatting about that, she
OL,18,Fexplained how she was there, why she
OL,19,Fwas there.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1777471868
OL,3,CMum-of-five says riots were 'worst two
OL,4,Cseconds of my life, but I'm sorry'
OL,6,F"She was sorry for what she'd done,
OL,7,Fthat she couldn't believe that she'd
OL,8,Fdone what she'd done, and she was just
OL,9,Fout of it really, and that really
OL,10,Fhelped, massively."
OL,12,FStacey is slowly turning her life
OL,13,Faround and says she has learned
OL,14,Flessons from the experience.
OL,16,F"I'm just grateful I've had the
OL,17,Fopportunity to meet (the victims of
OL,18,Fthe riots) and say sorry," she added.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1777471868
OL,3,CMum-of-five says riots were 'worst two
OL,4,Cseconds of my life, but I'm sorry'
OL,6,F"It's not just like the houses and the
OL,7,Fmaterial things, it's the long-term
OL,8,Feffect it's going to have.
OL,10,F"Like people need to consider, like
OL,11,Ftake that into account as well, so I'm
OL,12,Fjust grateful that I've had the
OL,13,Fopportunity to let people know that
OL,14,FI'm not racist, I'm not going to hurt
OL,15,Fnobody, I don't want no agro or
OL,16,Fnothing, like I'm just myself."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
